data.title: 910 W Johanna St, Austin, TX 78704
data.meta_description: Zillow has 40 photos of this $3,790,000 4 beds, 4 baths, 3,076 Square Feet single family home located at 910 W Johanna St, Austin, TX 78704 built in 2021. MLS #2819990.
data.text: This contemporary luxury inspired by Australian architecture and designed by Breckstudio Architecture is guaranteed to leave you awe-inspired. This exquisite 4-bedroom, 4-bathroom home with 3076 square feet is crafted to seamlessly blend indoor and outdoor spaces. Showcasing an impressive 30' wide span of 10' tall Western sliders and windows unveil your own private backyard sanctuary, complete with a large pool, hot tub and seating areas. A kitchen that steals the spotlight, anchoring the open-concept kitchen/living/dining space, highlights custom cabinetry, an oversized island with waterfall countertops, 13.5' wood-cladded ceilings and an intimate gas fireplace. ?The first-floor master suite has direct pool/hot tub access, along with a private courtyard and outdoor shower from the master bathroom. Upstairs, a large lounge complete with a wet bar and beverage refrigerator provides additional entertainment space and sweeping downtown views of the Austin skyline, featuring a 16.5' three-tier slider extending out to an oversized patio. A large side yard with endless possibilities can be used for RV parking or added green space. With its meticulous design details and purposeful layout, this home is guaranteed to be one of the most captivating residences you'll encounter in 78704.
